,Recommended,528660,34135534,Posted: 9 August,all,Croof046,"Spin rush is a simple game for a low price. You rotate a colored square/Hexagon to match up with a colored ball coming towards you, the longer you last the more points you get. Graphics are designed to distract you with flashes movements and bright colors, especially so on ""Trip"" mode, where the cube and balls also rapidly phase between colors. Not a huge amount of content, but a few different game modes keeps it interesting for a little while. I would recommend you grab this on sale or in a bundle, if it sounds like your cup of tea."
